docs {
  # Create Swipe
  
  Records a swipe action and creates a match if mutual like is detected.
  
  ## Body Parameters
  - `swiperId` (required) - ID of the user performing the swipe
  - `swipedUserId` (required) - ID of the user being swiped on
  - `direction` (required) - "like" | "pass" | "superlike"
  
  ## Response
  ```json
  {
    "swipeId": "uuid",
    "matched": false,
    "matchId": null
  }
  ```
  
  If mutual like detected:
  ```json
  {
    "swipeId": "uuid",
    "matched": true,
    "matchId": "uuid"
  }
  ```
}
